    },
    {
      "id": "68859c3800000000008c6ac0",
      "text": "[北朝鮮による日本人拉致問題]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1753586744,
      "updated": 1753586881
    },
    {
      "id": "68859cb600000000008c6ac3",
      "text": " 陰謀論だと思われていたが、事実だった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1753586871,
      "updated": 1753586910
    },
    {
      "id": "68859cc200000000008c6ac4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1753586882,
      "updated": 1753586882
    },
    {
      "id": "699ad0eb000000000097c6a9",
      "text": "[オウム真理教事件]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771753707,
      "updated": 1771753733
    },
    {
      "id": "699ad112000000000097c6ab",
      "text": " 陰謀論だと思われていたが、本当に国家転覆を計るカルト集団だった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771753747,
